snippet.title: MEN are DYING! Scientist's Reveal Men's Y-CHROMOSOME is in DANGER
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo to simplify your Business - https://www.odoo.com/r/Oum 

Humanity faces a significant threat: according to recent scientific research, men may be on the verge of extinction, with adverse effects on women as well. Recently, you may have heard reports, widely circulated in the news, about a serious illness affecting men at the DNA level, potentially leading to their disappearance.
A recent study from Kansas State University found that the genetic data of the Y chromosome, which is present only in males, is diminishing with each generation. This is alarming! But why is this happening only to men? Why aren‚Äôt women experiencing similar changes in their genes? Interestingly, women's DNA is becoming stronger and healthier with each generation. So, does this mean life on Earth could end due to this male-specific decline? Is life fundamentally born with a fatal flaw? Could that flaw be death itself? Let's discuss...

Kaffara Episode 54 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 18th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Kaffara Episode 53 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 18th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What's it feel like to die? From director Bong Joon Ho, comes Mickey 17 - only in theaters January 31, 2025. #Mickey17  

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the job‚Ä¶ to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, ‚ÄúMickey 17‚Äù stars Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúTenet‚Äù), Naomi Ackie (‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù), Steven Yeun (‚ÄúNope‚Äù), with Academy Award nominees Toni Collette (‚ÄúHereditary‚Äù), and Mark Ruffalo (‚ÄúPoor Things‚Äù). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner (Oscar winner for ‚ÄúMoonlight,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù), Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winner for ‚ÄúMoonlight,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù ‚ÄúSnowpiercer‚Äù). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúBardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúThe Favourite,‚Äù ‚ÄúCruella‚Äù). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for ‚ÄúParasite,‚Äù ‚ÄúOkja‚Äù). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,‚Äù ‚ÄúFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw‚Äù). The costume designer is Catherine George (‚ÄúOkja,‚Äù Snowpiercer‚Äù). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: ‚ÄúMickey 17.‚Äù The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on January 31, 2025, and internationally beginning on 28 January 2025.

snippet.title: RED SNAPPER FISH | Big Fish Grill Recipe Cooking in Village | Fish Fry in Clay | Ancient Cooking
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook fish recipe using big red snapper fish. We grill this fish using clay. First, we apply the hand-ground traditional masala on the fish then we wrap it with banana leaf and silver foil paper and finally we cover the fish with clay. We directly grill the fish in the fire. 

Finally, we tasted the fish with a nice aroma! Tate is yummy!

FOR BESAN BATTER 
3 Tbsp Besan 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
Water as Needed 


FOR MIXTURE 
1 Cup Poha 
4 Boiled Potatoes 
1 Onion 
1 Carrot 
5 - 6 Beans 
1/2 Cup Peas

2 tsp Salt 
1 tsp Coriander Powder

1/2 tsp Ajwain 
1 tsp Pizza / Oregano Seasoning 
1 tsp Red Chilli Flakes 
Fresh Coriander Leaves 

BREAD CRUMBS AS NEEDED

Tera jigra

Tera jigra

Uth kudiye

Uth kudiye

Tu zindagi ka dariya hai
Toofano se ladh jave tera jigra

Tu zindagi ka dariya hai
Toofano se ladh jave tera jigra

Faulaad ka dil ban jayenge

Uth kudiye

Uth kudiye

Naa hai zameen na hai falak

Kuch aur nahi hai zindagi
Bas intihaan dar intihaan
Kuch aur nahi hai zindagi

snippet.description:
#coconut  #climbing  #climbingmachine #innovation 

In this video, we showcase an innovative coconut plucking tool designed by Benin Lal Kingsley from Kanyakumari. With the growing challenges faced by farmers, such as labor shortages, this modern tool offers a practical solution. The tool's standout feature is that it allows coconuts to be plucked without needing to climb the tree, making the process safer and more efficient. This is an example of how new agricultural technologies are revolutionizing farming, providing much-needed relief to farmers and boosting productivity. Watch the video to see how this tool works and its potential benefits for coconut farmers.

#coconut  #climbing  #climbingmachine #innovation 

In this video, we showcase an innovative coconut plucking tool designed by Benin Lal Kingsley from Kanyakumari. With the growing challenges faced by farmers, such as labor shortages, this modern tool offers a practical solution. The tool's standout feature is that it allows coconuts to be plucked without needing to climb the tree, making the process safer and more efficient. This is an example of how new agricultural technologies are revolutionizing farming, providing much-needed relief to farmers and boosting productivity. Watch the video to see how this tool works and its potential benefits for coconut farmers.

snippet.title: Why 40% WORLD POPULATION Live in Only 2 Countries
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo to simplify your Business - https://www.odoo.com/r/yQYN

In terms of population, India and China alone have more people than the combined total of all other 170 countries on Earth!  The world seems very crowded, and many experts suggest we need to control population growth. Even Elon Musk is talking about moving to Mars because of this issue.
However, if you look at the world population map, you'll see that most of the planet is still uninhabited. In Asia, India and China together house 2.7 billion people, or 36% of the world‚Äôs population. So, why do these two countries, located on the same continent, hold such a significant portion of the global population? Is their geographical location a key factor? Let's discuss.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.
